Package: hdlbrgdown
Title: A package for creating PhD theses at the Faculty of Bioscience at 
    Heidelberg University using R Markdown
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Christian H.", "Holland", 
    email = "cholland2408@gmail.com", 
    role = c("cre", "aut"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3060-5786")))
Description: Using the bookdown package and LaTeX and Word thesis templates from
    Reed College, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well.
URL: https://github.com/christianholland/hdlbrgdown
BugReports: https://github.com/christianholland/hdlbrgdown/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    remotes,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - http://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
